          <span class="animate">
            <p>Hey, I'm Drew.</p>

            <p>
              I'm currently a Senior Research Software Engineer at
              <Link external href="https://www.hartree.stfc.ac.uk/">
                STFC Hartree Centre
              </Link>, part of the <Link
                external
                href="https://www.ukri.org/councils/stfc/"
              >
                Science and Technology Facilities Council (STFC)
              </Link>
              which is in turn part of <Link
                external
                href="https://www.ukri.org/"
              >
                UK Research and Innovation (UKRI)
              </Link>. I live in Liverpool and work in <Link
                external
                href="https://www.ukri.org/who-we-are/stfc/facilities/daresbury-laboratory/"
              >
                Daresbury Laboratory
              </Link>, near Warrington.
            </p>
