          <span class="animate">
            <p>
              I'm interesting in all things technical, but I've got a particular
              interest in things like databases, programming languages, best
              practices, cloud infrastructure and game development.
            </p>

            <p>
              I like using and writing about languages like Go, Python,
              TypeScript and Rust, but I'll use whatever tool is best for the
              task at hand.
            </p>
